org.opendaylight.controller.sal.core

Class Node.NodeIDType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.sal.core.Node.NodeIDType
  • Enclosing class:
    Node

    public static final class Node.NodeIDType
extends java.lang.Object
    Enum-like static class created with the purpose of identifing multiple type of nodes in the SDN network. The type is necessary to figure out to later on correctly use the nodeID. Using a static class instead of an Enum so we can add dynamically new types without changing anything in the surround.
